#a course of action thought to be [[prudent]] or [[advantageous]]; hence [[prudence]] or [[sagacity]]
#* Honesty is the best '''policy'''
#a [[contract]]  of [[insurance]]
#* Your insurance '''policy''' covers fire and theft only.
